     C                     MOVE F3KTRT    H2LOC2
     C                     MOVE F3KTRR    H2LOC3
     C                     MOVE F3KTRD    H2LOC4
     C                     END
     C*
     C                     ELSE
TCHK3C                     MOVEL*BLANK    F3ZETI
