     C                     MOVE BANUKE    I2DOCK           DOCK CODE
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    I2DUMY           DUMMY
     C                     MOVE PNONY     I2DELY           DELIVERY
     C                     MOVE PNKOJ     I2FACT           FACTORY
     C                     MOVE PNUKE     I2DOCK           DOCK
